VersionedEntityMixin.__description__:
Mixin for versioning and history tracking.

Attributes:
    version (int): Version number of the entity.
    created_at (datetime): Creation timestamp.
    updated_at (datetime): Last update timestamp.
    change_log (List[str]): Log of changes made to the entity.
    version_history (List[VersionControl]): List of version control history entries.
VersionedEntityMixin.change_log__description__: Log of changes made to the entity
VersionedEntityMixin.version_history__description__: List of version control history entries
